@DavidHDev current schema for the manifest metadata. Let me know what you think right now it is heavily inspired by the package.json meta keys.

```ts
type Meta = {
    builtAt: number;
    authors?: string[] | undefined;
    description?: string | undefined;
    repository?: string | undefined;
    homepage?: string | undefined;
    tags?: string[] | undefined;
    bugs?: string | undefined;
}
```
